  • java.lang.Object

    Commentable

    public class Playlist
extends java.lang.Object
implements Commentable
    This class represents a playlist, which can be created by a creator.
    Author:
    Alexander Trahe, Benjamin Knauer, Tobias
    Invariant:
    A playlist contains at least 1 medium.

      • removeMedium

        public void removeMedium(Medium medium)
        Completely removes a medium from the playlist. (meaning also multiple existing ones)
        Parameters:
        medium - medium which should be completely removed from the playlist
        Precondition:
        mediumList is not empty
        Postcondition:
        mediumLists size is reduced by 1

      • move

        public void move(int currentPos,

        This method moves a mediaobject from it's current position to a new one.

        newPos - The position the mediaobject is supposed to be moved to.

        Postcondition:
